{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/line-up-form-elements-responsively-with-bootstrap","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"bootstrap","demoType":null,"title":"Rasporedi elemente forme koji se prilagođavaju uređaju koristeći Bootstrap","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada smo spremni da rasporedimo elemente vaše forme <code>input</code> i vaš podnesak <code>button</code> u jednoj liniji. To ćemo uraditi na isti način kao što smo ranije: korišćenjem elementa <code>div</code> koji ima klasu <code>row</code>, i drugih elemenata <code>div</code> unutar njega koji koriste klasu <code>col-xs-*</code>.</p>\n<p>Umestite tekst forme vašeg <code>input</code> i dugme za slanje <code>button</code> unutar <code>div</code> koje ima klasu <code>row</code>. Umestite tekst forme vašeg <code>input</code> unutar diva sa klasom <code>col-xs-7</code>. Umestite dugme za slanje vaše forme <code>button</code> u <code>div</code> koje ima klasu <code>col-xs-5</code>.</p>\n<p>Ovo je poslednji izazov koji ćemo raditi za sada za Cat Photo App. Nadamo se da ste uživali u učenju Font Awesome, Bootstrap, i responzivnog dizajna!</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aec908845","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18225,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/bootstrap/line-up-form-elements-responsively-with-bootstrap"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.2.0/css/font-awesome.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lobster\" rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\">\r\n<style>\r\n  h2 {\r\n    font-family: Lobster, Monospace;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n  .thick-green-border {\r\n    border-color: green;\r\n    border-width: 10px;\r\n    border-style: solid;\r\n    border-radius: 50%;\r\n  }\r\n\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-8\">\r\n      <h2 class=\"text-primary text-center\">CatPhotoApp</h2>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <a href=\"#\"><img class=\"img-responsive thick-green-border\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/relaxing-cat.jpg\" alt=\"A cute orange cat lying on its back.\"></a>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/cat-photo-app/running-cats.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Tuxedo cats running on dirt ground.\">\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-thumbs-up\"></i> Like</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-info\"><i class=\"fa fa-info-circle\"></i> Info</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n      <button class=\"btn btn-block btn-danger\"><i class=\"fa fa-trash\"></i> Delete</button>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <p>Things cats <span class=\"text-danger\">love:</span></p>\r\n  <ul>\r\n    <li>catnip</li>\r\n    <li>laser pointers</li>\r\n    <li>lasagna</li>\r\n  </ul>\r\n  <p>Top 3 things cats hate:</p>\r\n  <ol>\r\n    <li>flea treatment</li>\r\n    <li>thunder</li>\r\n    <li>other cats</li>\r\n  </ol>\r\n  <form action=\"https://freecatphotoapp.com/submit-cat-photo\">\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Indoor</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"radio\" name=\"indoor-outdoor\"> Outdoor</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"row\">\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Loving</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Lazy</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"col-xs-4\">\r\n        <label><input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"personality\"> Crazy</label>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\" placeholder=\"cat photo URL\" required>\r\n    <button type=\"submit\" class=\"btn btn-primary\"><i class=\"fa fa-paper-plane\"></i> Submit</button>\r\n  </form>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Tvoje dugme za slanje forme i polje za unos teksta treba da budu postavljeni unutar div-a sa klasom <code>row</code>.</p>","testString":"const textInput = document.querySelectorAll('div.row input[type=\"text\"]'); \r\nconst submitInput = document.querySelectorAll('div.row button[type=\"submit\"]');\r\nassert.lengthOf(textInput,1);\r\nassert.lengthOf(submitInput, 1);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoje polje za unos teksta treba da bude postavljeno unutar div-a sa klasom <code>col-xs-7</code>.</p>","testString":"const textInput = document.querySelectorAll('div.col-xs-7 input[type=\"text\"]'); \r\nassert.lengthOf(textInput ,1);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoje dugme za slanje forme treba da bude postavljeno unutar div-a sa klasom <code>col-xs-5</code>.</p>","testString":"const submitInput  = document.querySelectorAll('div.col-xs-5 button[type=\"submit\"]'); \r\nassert.lengthOf(submitInput ,1);"},{"text":"<p>Svi <code>div</code> elementi treba da imaju zatvarajuće oznake.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/<\\/div>/g);\r\nassert.match(code,/<div/g);\r\n\r\nassert.equal(code.match(/<\\/div>/g).length,code.match(/<div/g).length);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/le